title: Luis J Gomez - Fighting Cab Drivers
description: We're joined by stand up comedian and podcaster Luis J Gomez. Luis talks about fights with cab drivers, buying weapons as a kid, and the coronavirus. You may know Luis J Gomez from Joe Rogan Podcast, Legion of Skanks, Believe You Me, Real Ass Podcast.
